#

Birnentart (Pear Tart)

60 min
$15
250 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 8

Allergens:

GlutenEggs

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianNut-free

Cuisine:

AmericanFrench

Course:

Dessert

Tags:

DessertEasyQuick

Description

A delightful and easy pear tart that brings the sweetness of ripe pears together with a flaky crust, perfect for any dessert lover!

Ingredients

  • puff pastry: 1 sheet
  • pears: 3 medium, peeled and sliced
  • sugar: 1/4 cup
  • ground cinnamon: 1/2 tsp
  • vanilla extract: 1 tsp
  • lemon juice: 1 tbsp
  • egg (for egg wash): 1
